OL,6,FVictims have found themselves unable
OL,7,Fto switch to more affordable rates
OL,8,Fbecause of tough borrowing criteria.
OL,10,FMs Wray said: "I'm 42 still living
OL,11,Fwith my parents, due to not being able
OL,12,Fto pay the full mortgage payments
OL,13,Fbecause they went up so much.
OL,15,F"Unfortunately my credit rating is now
OL,16,Fshot so it's going to be another six
OL,17,Fyears before I can even look at buying
OL,18,Fsomewhere.
