OL,6,FThey have contacted the production
OL,7,Fteam behind the ITVX drama Mr Bates vs
OL,8,Fthe Post Office, which was credited
OL,9,Fwith raising the profile of the
OL,10,Fhundreds of subpostmasters and
OL,11,Fsubpostmistresses who were wrongly
OL,12,Fconvicted of fraud.
