OL,6,FMr Poynton said the interest rate on
OL,7,Fhis mortgage has doubled in the last
OL,8,Fyear, going up to 8.2%. He is
OL,9,Fconcerned it could increase further.
OL,11,FMr Poynton said: "We constantly get
OL,12,Fdiscredited, (people saying) that it
OL,13,Fwas our own fault.
OL,15,F"Yes, we took the loans on and
OL,16,Fpossibly got bad advice but is it fair
OL,17,Fthat we are having to pay over those
OL,18,Fodds to an inactive lender?
