OL,6,F"The due diligence wasn't done by the
OL,7,Fgovernment at the time when our
OL,8,Fmortgages were sold."
OL,10,FOlivia Selley, lawyer at Harcus
OL,11,FParker, said: "People are actively
OL,12,Fliving in fear of repossession. The
OL,13,Flevels of stress, anxiety and
OL,14,Fdepression particularly among our
OL,15,Fclient book are very, very high.
